name: Standard Staggered Picture Frame
description:
I build photo frames from smaller photo frames.

These are straight or wonky staggered frames to make a bigger multi-frame picture!

Very unique.

To buy these in most shops can be very expensive.

Many sizes of frames available for your photos.

Individual frame sizes are;
SMALL 10x15cm (4x6")
MEDIUM 13x18cm (5x7")
LARGE 18x24cm (7x9.5")
X LARGE 21x30cm (fits A4 pictures or 4x '4x6' pictures!)

Any final frame size can be built (within reason)

Many colours to choose from;
BLACK
WHITE
RED
PINK
LIGHT BLUE
DARK BLUE
GREEN

Message me for a tailored design, I can do all SMALL frames or all LARGE frames!
All one colour or any mixture of colours from the selection above!
 
Or just click to buy now for similar to what's in the pictures!

The standard buy now product contains;
2 LARGE
4 MEDIUM
4 SMALL frames
all in a standard straight configuration like in the picture.

If you order a 'other' or 'other mixed' version, please contact me to advise your chosen colour combination!

THANKS!
